'''Lqʷran''' nɣ '''Lquran''' nɣ '''Quran''' ( s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|taɛrabt]] : '''القرآن''' —''Al qu'ran''  neɣ '''القرآن الكريم'''''—Al-qur'an al-karim'' ) iga aḍris asgdan akkʷ ilan atig ɣ [[Lislam]]. Ar ttinnin insllmn is iga awal n rbbi d is d netta ad t-id-issugzn f urqqas nns [[Muḥmmad]]. Ar ass-ad, adlis ad iga adlis amzwaru d udlis aqbur akkʷ ittawsan is ittyura s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|tutlayt taɛrabt]]. 

flsn akkʷ imuslmn d inflas(imumnn) s is iga lqqʷran awal n rbbi isggizt-id s ils aɛṛab lmubin, f umazan{{note|a}} [[Muḥmmad|Muḥammad]] {{saw}} s ubrid n lmalak Jibril ɣ kigan n tmldawin zɣ lbiɛta nns ɣ usggʷas 610 ar tamttant-nns ɣ wass n 8 yunyu 632. Ibḍa Lqqʷran f 114 n tassurt, illa gis 6236 n layat. Illa ɣ Lquran ifyar (layat) imakkiyn d tiyyaḍ imadaniyn. Lquran lkarim iga adlis amggaru zɣ idlisn n ṛbbi, issggʷiz-t rbbi f nbi [[Muḥmmad|Muḥammad]] {{saw}}. D tilawat n lquran d ussfld nns d twuri sis gan kullu lɛibadat ar sisn ittaẓ umuslm i rbbi bac ayzddig ul nns. Tssnti tɣrma n imuslmn dffir ma iggiz Lquran s wakal. 

